      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASHBY GNOCCHI (1) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 520m behind Major Flirt (30.37) in a Grade 5. Looks the one to beat on her best form. MRS. BUTTONS (2) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 29.88 beating Natisa's Secret. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Will go close again if runs up to latest. RITZA OLD MATE (3) has missed the frame at his last two runs but could not have been more impressive the run prior in his enormous 29.49 win at The Gardens over 515m. Expecting another bold showing. RUGGED ETHICS (8) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
